    <item>
      <title>巴拿马考虑取消与香港亿万富翁公司的港口交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴拿马正在考虑是否取消与运营巴拿马运河附近港口的香港公司的合同，此举可能是为了化解唐纳德·特朗普总统关于对抗中国在这条关键水道周围影响力的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/panama-said-to-mull-canceling-port-deal-with-hong-kong-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
